Regression Analysis:
Regression Analysis is a supervised machine learning technique used to predict a continuous numerical value based on one or more input features. It helps understand the relationship between dependent and independent variables and is widely used for forecasting and prediction.

Applications
🏠 House Price Prediction
📈 Stock Price Forecasting
🌡️ Weather Prediction
💰 Sales Forecasting
🚗 Car Price Prediction
🏥 Medical Cost Prediction
